### ResourceCenter V2 API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 查询资源中心分组
# 预期分组：catalogs / tenant-applications / instances / releases / runtime-contexts / runtime-executions / datasources / audit-summary / debug-entries
# 返回 ResourceCenterGroupsResponse：{ groups: [...], warnings: [...] }
# 当个别应用实例未绑定可用数据源时，接口仍返回 200，并在 warnings 中给出被跳过实例提示
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/resource-center/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询数据源双层消费模型（平台级/应用级）
# 响应包含每个数据源的 bindingRelations 明细（bindingId/bindingType/isActive/source）
# 同时包含治理字段：isOrphan/isDuplicate/isInvalid/isUnbound/impactScope/repairSuggestion
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/resource-center/datasource-consumption
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 禁用无效绑定
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/resource-center/datasource-consumption/repair/disable-invalid-binding
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{login.response.headers.X-CSRF-TOKEN}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bindingId": "1"
}

### 切换主绑定
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/resource-center/datasource-consumption/repair/switch-primary-binding
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{login.response.headers.X-CSRF-TOKEN}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantAppInstanceId": "1",
  "targetDataSourceId": "1",
  "note": "repair-switch"
}

### 解绑孤儿绑定
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/resource-center/datasource-consumption/repair/unbind-orphan-binding
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{login.response.headers.X-CSRF-TOKEN}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bindingId": "1"
}
